<h1>
  Data Types</h1>
<p>
  Data types are the basic building blocks for Java. Similar to Lego bricks, data types vary in size which determine the amount of storage it needs. By combining different data types, we can develop systems like a small cafe management tool or a complex system like Google search or OpenAI.</p>
<p>
  Computer stores data in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Binary_number">binaries</a> which are just 0s and 1s. It needs a way to specify that this data is a number and this data is a letter. Consider this receipt as an illustration. What type of data is needed to saved this information?</p>
