<p>
In terms of how the system will store the data of the receipt, the system can use <code class="inline">int</code> to denote the quantity of each line item and the table number. Similarly, <code class="inline">long</code> is more suitable for the check number as this number may get get big.</p>
<br>
<h3>
Decimals</h3>
<p>
Numbers with fractions can be represented with float or double.</p>
